{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"BUT 멤버","body":"후후, 아무튼 엄청 오랜만이네.\n레코딩 때는 여러 가지로 도움받았는데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"아닙니다, 저야말로 신세만 졌습니다~\n오늘은 무슨 일이십니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev199-ep3-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"BUT 멤버","body":"밴드의 새로운 아티스트 사진을 찍으러 왔어.\n마야 짱은…… 의상을 보니까 일 때문에 왔어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"네! 오늘은 잡지 촬영이 있어서 치사토 씨하고…… 아앗!?\n죄, 죄송합니다 치사토 씨, 소개도 안 해 드리고……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev199-ep3-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"후후, 괜찮아.\n마야 짱이 아는 사람…… 이지?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characte